contentfulProduct.name: Chicken Paté
contentfulProduct.teaser: Chicken Paté with freshly deboned meat, grainfree, complete and balanced wetfood for kittens, pregnant cats and nursing mothers.

ingredients.ingredients: 85% fresh chicken meat, chicken liver and meat products, 9,5% fresh salmon, plant products, vitamins & minerals.

analysis.analysis: Protein 8,5%, Fat content 6%, Crude ash 2%, Crude fibre 0.4%, Moisture 80%.

feedingRecommendation.feedingRecommendation: Freshwater should always be available. Prior to opening the pack,  it should be stored in dry, cool conditions. After opening, store in an airtight container, keep refrigerated and use it within 72 Hours. The recommended quantities can vary according to breed, seasonal and age factors. Traceability: Best before date/lot no, see can bottom.

nutritionAdditives.nutritionAdditives: Vitamin A 2000IU/kg, Vitamin D3 200IU/kg , Vitamin E 20IU/kg, Zinc (Zinc Sulphate Monohydrate) 10 mg/kg, Manganese (Manganous Sulphate Monohydrate) 5 mg/kg, Selenium (Sodium Selenite) 0.04 mg/kg, Iodine (Calcium iodate anhydrous) 0.50 mg/kg, Taurine 250 mg/kg.

longDescription.longDescription:
Chef’s Choice Chicken Recipe For Kittens is carefully formulated by chefs and nutritionists to provide the extra energy kittens need in the form of calories, fat and protein to fuel all of their growing, playing and discovering. Our smooth kitten recipe is made with 100% fresh chicken and natural, wholesome ingredients free from grains, sugar, salt, artificial colors, aromas or preservatives. This mouth watering recipe is enhanced with vitamins, minerals and other nutrients to make this meal hard to forget. 
You might be cooking your own food but your cat has a Chef at home.
